subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: The defending champion Carlos Moyá needed nearly three hours to eliminate Serbia’s Viktor Troicki, prevailing by 3-6, 7-6 (2), 7-5 to reach the quarterfinals at the ATP Croatia Open in Umag.
